<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1190.109539.figure10>
    dc:description "Figure 10. Amara (Curtonotus) harpaloides A dorsal habitus, male (Zhangbei, Hebei) B pronotum posterior angle (Tianjun, Qinghai) C male mesotibia D lateral view of aedeagus E right paramere F apical lamella G female gonocoxite (Yongdeng, Gansu). Scale bar: 5 mm (A); 1 mm (B-E); 0.5 mm (F, G)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/971806" ;
